üé® WEEK 2 ‚Äì DAY 4 Bootstrap | Complete Guide

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üåê What is Bootstrap?

**Bootstrap** is a **popular CSS framework** used to build **responsive, mobile-first websites quickly**.

* Saves development time
* Pre-built CSS & JS components
* Works with HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* Widely used in industry

üìå Bootstrap = ready-made UI + responsiveness

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üöÄ Why Use Bootstrap?

* Mobile-first design
* No need to write CSS from scratch
* Consistent UI
* Fast prototyping
* Industry standard

---

üß© Bootstrap Versions

* Bootstrap 3 ‚Üí old
* Bootstrap 4 ‚Üí improved
* **Bootstrap 5 ‚Üí latest & recommended**

  * No jQuery dependency
  * Better grid & utilities

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚öôÔ∏è How to Add Bootstrap

1Ô∏è‚É£ Using CDN (Most Common)

```html
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
```

---

2Ô∏è‚É£ Download Bootstrap

* Download files
* Link CSS & JS manually

---

üì¶ Bootstrap Container

Used to wrap website content.

```html
<div class="container">Content</div>
<div class="container-fluid">Full width</div>
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üß± Bootstrap Grid System (Very Important)

Bootstrap uses a **12-column grid system**.

Grid Structure

```html
<div class="row">
  <div class="col">Column</div>
  <div class="col">Column</div>
</div>
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üì± Responsive Grid Breakpoints

| Class   | Screen Size |
| ------- | ----------- |
| col-    | Extra small |
| col-sm- | ‚â•576px      |
| col-md- | ‚â•768px      |
| col-lg- | ‚â•992px      |
| col-xl- | ‚â•1200px     |

Example:

```html
<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">Box</div>
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üé® Bootstrap Typography

```html
<h1 class="text-primary">Heading</h1>
<p class="text-muted">Paragraph</p>
```

Text utilities:

* `text-center`
* `text-start`
* `text-end`
* `fw-bold`
* `fst-italic`

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üéØ Bootstrap Colors

```html
text-primary
text-success
text-danger
bg-warning
bg-dark
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üîò Bootstrap Buttons

```html
<button class="btn btn-primary">Primary</button>
<button class="btn btn-success">Success</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-danger">Delete</button>
```

Button sizes:

* `btn-sm`
* `btn-lg`

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üÉè Bootstrap Cards

```html
<div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">Card Title</h5>
    <p class="card-text">Card content</p>
  </div>
</div>
```

üìå Used for product cards, profiles, blogs

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üß≠ Bootstrap Navbar

```html
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
  <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">MySite</a>
</nav>
```

‚úî Responsive
‚úî Collapsible menu

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üìù Bootstrap Forms

```html
<form>
  <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter name">
</form>
```

Form classes:

* `form-control`
* `form-label`
* `form-check`

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üìä Bootstrap Tables

```html
<table class="table table-bordered table-striped">
  <tr><th>Name</th></tr>
  <tr><td>User</td></tr>
</table>
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üß© Bootstrap Utilities (Very Powerful)

Spacing

```html
m-3   /* margin */
p-2   /* padding */
```

Display

```html
d-flex
d-none
```

Flex Utilities

```html
d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üé¨ Bootstrap JavaScript Components

Requires Bootstrap JS bundle.

Components:

* Modal
* Dropdown
* Carousel
* Tooltip
* Accordion

Example Modal Trigger:

```html
<button data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#myModal">Open</button>
```

---

üì± Bootstrap Responsive Design

* Mobile-first approach
* Automatically adapts to screen size
* No media queries needed in most cases

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üÜö Bootstrap vs Custom CSS

| Bootstrap        | Custom CSS   |
| ---------------- | ------------ |
| Fast development | Full control |
| Pre-built UI     | More code    |
| Consistent       | Flexible     |

üìå Real projects use **both**

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚ùå Common Bootstrap Mistakes

* Overusing classes
* Ignoring grid system
* Mixing Bootstrap & custom CSS badly
* Not understanding utilities

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

üí° Best Practices

* Use Bootstrap for layout
* Customize using your own CSS
* Follow grid system properly
* Keep HTML clean

